@base = http://localhost:3000
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Health check
GET {{base}}/health

### ─────────────────────────────────────
### AUTH
### ─────────────────────────────────────

### Registrar usuario
# @name register
POST {{base}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sergio",
  "email": "sergio@example.com",
  "password": "Password1"
}

###

### Iniciar sesión
# @name login
POST {{base}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "sergio@example.com",
  "password": "Password1"
}

###

### Perfil del usuario autenticado
GET {{base}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─────────────────────────────────────
### ROOMS
### ─────────────────────────────────────

### Listar salas
GET {{base}}/api/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear sala
# @name createRoom
POST {{base}}/api/rooms
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "general",
  "description": "Sala general de chat"
}

###

### Historial de mensajes de una sala
GET {{base}}/api/rooms/{{createRoom.response.body.data._id}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
